description: The ESOU has established that an ancient Doomsday Prophecy involving the return of the Mayan God of the Underworld, Bolon Yokte K'u, is underway. But, the ESOU also believes this doomsday scenario may have played out some 5,000 years ago in and failed. Now the ESOU is in a race against time to find out what they can do in present time to stop the prophecy...
name: Foam of the Sea

description: Before Natasha assembles with the Avengers Initiative, see her in this hard-hitting espionage adventure set between the events of IRON MAN 2 and MARVELS THE AVENGERS!
name: Part Three

volume.name: The Avengers Prelude: Black Widow Strikes

description:
Garth Ennis (PUNISHER MAX, Preacher) and Goran Parlov (PUNISHER MAX) continue to put Nick Fury through hell.

Fury, knee deep in the messy quagmire that is French Indochina in the 1950s, faces a war unlike any he has ever seen.

Witness the most brutal battle ever put on a comic book page!
name: My War Gone By Issue 3: And Some People Left for Heaven Without Warning

description: For a long time now, society has sensationalized and profited off bad behavior. DeadZone catches wind that some stolen evidence, the swimsuit that a small child was murdered in, is being trafficked by collectors of the odd and macabre. DeadZone is about to end this transaction right down to the final buyeruntil he finds out who the buyer actually is.
name: Can Anyone Stop Murderabilia?

description:
IDW's newly recolored reprints of classic Doctor Who tales from years past, this time featuring the SIXTH DOCTOR, continues! The Doctor, Peri, and Frobisher find themselves under attack on dormant colony ship in 'Profits of Doom!'

Originally printed in Doctor Who Magazine #120-122.
name: Profits of Doom!

description: With strange eons, even death may die, unleashing ancient horrors upon our world. They rise from the abyss or descend from the stars, caring no more for our existence than we care for the random atoms about us. Yet there are those who dare to strap on their brass and leather, shoulder their plasmotic rifles and stoke up the boilers to their super-cannons, land crawlers, submersibles and airships. Steam WILL save the world!
name: Steamcraft

description: In the sweltering summer, the boiler room is too stuffy, and a full explorer's kit can give even the most intrepid a case of heatstroke. Time to loosen up the leather and unbuckle the brass, and seek adventure in the surf and sand, or the nearest natatorium! (All while maintaining decorum so as not to shame Her Majesty, of course.)
name: Steampunk Swimsuit
